<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="a6Dec1925"><font color="red">6 December 1925</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver from Lucia Joyce): My father &hellip; passed a rather good night and to-day to everybody&apos;s astonishment he seems much better than he has ever been on the day following an operation &hellip; My mother was against the operation as he had been working so hard for the past three months </div>
